resourceAbstractObject.default: Data from the 'Mediterranean forest ecosystem observatory' (FORET): Observatory of Mediterranean forest ecosystems and vulnerability to climate change: gas and energy exchanges, growth, plant and animal dynamics, .... This observatory is part of the Montpellier Research Observatory of Environment (OSU OREME, oreme.org). It is labelized in the framework of TGIR ICOS. It consists in different observing tasks: Fires ; GMAP ; Puéchabon.
